    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "There is but little real, genuine, devoted, pure love. This precious article is very rare. Passion is termed love.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"2T 381.1\" data-link=\"120.1653\">Testimonies for the Church 2:381</span>.</span></a></sup>",
