    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Love is a plant of heavenly growth, and it must be fostered and nourished. Affectionate hearts, truthful, loving words, will make happy families and exert an elevating influence upon all who come within the sphere of their influence.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">4<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"4T 548.1\" data-link=\"114.2701\">Testimonies for the Church 4:548</span>.</span></a></sup>",
