    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The young are bewitched with the mania for courtship and marriage. Lovesick sentimentalism prevails. Great vigilance and tact are needed to guard the youth from these wrong influences.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">11<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"5T 59.4\" data-link=\"113.297\">Ibid., 5:60</span>.</span></a></sup>",
