    "refcode_long": "The Adventist Home, p. 54.1 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The holiness of the oracles of God is not loved by very many who claim to be Bible Christians. They show by their free, loose conduct that they prefer a wider scope. They do not want their selfish indulgences limited.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">15<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 14, 1888\" data-link=\"14055.4119001\">Manuscript 14, 1888</span>.</span></a></sup>",
